22#include "mpc-impl.h"
23
24/* return 0 iff a = b */
25int
26mpc_cmp_si_si (mpc_srcptr a, long int b, long int c)
27{
28 int cmp_re, cmp_im;
29
30 cmp_re = mpfr_cmp_si (mpc_realref(a), b);
31 cmp_im = mpfr_cmp_si (mpc_imagref(a), c);
32
33 return MPC_INEX(cmp_re, cmp_im);
34}
